<item>
            <title>[DATAMONGO-928] Error when using field-naming-strategy-ref</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAMONGO-928</link>
                <project id="10701" key="DATAMONGO">Spring Data MongoDB</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt; org.springframework.beans.factory.parsing.BeanDefinitionParsingException: Configuration problem: Only one of the attributes abbreviate-field-names and field-naming-strategy-ref can be configured!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Occurs whenever field-naming-strategy-ref is used, possibly caused by abbreviate-field-names defaulting to false in the XSD:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;xsd:attribute name=&quot;abbreviate-field-names&quot; use=&quot;optional&quot; default=&quot;false&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
